dct_alternative_sm: Ryōtō Kaiwan (Liaotung Gulf) Approaches to Ryō Ga (Liao Ho) Entrance
dct_description_sm: Surveys of the Imperial Japanese Navy to 1937 ; U.S. Hydrographic Office Emergency Reproduction of Japanese Chart.
Depths shown by soundings and dotted lines; relief by contours and spot heights.
Shows coasts, low water areas, farmland, wetland, roads, buildings, city plan.
Map text in Japanese, with some latin script.
Japan Hydrographic Department seal in upper left margin.
